reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Guest Room Glow Up with These Industrial Gems!
reviews.reviewText: Let me tell you, these industrial table lamps are the perfect guest room glow-up! They're seriously high quality, with a sturdy base that feels like it could handle a rogue suitcase drop. Plus, they look fantastic! The seeded glass shades give off a warm, inviting light that makes the whole room feel cozy. Assembly was a breeze - I had them both put together in under 10 minutes, no tools required. Bonus points for the included LED bulbs, saved me a trip to the store! And speaking of bulbs, the dimming dial is a dream. It's super smooth, no annoying clicks or jumps, so you can find just the right brightness for any mood. My guests have been raving about them, and I can't blame them. These lamps are stylish, functional, and super easy to use. If you're looking for a touch of industrial charm for your bedroom, living room, or even your office, these are definitely worth checking out! Five stars, no doubt!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So cute, modern, and match bathroom lights
reviews.reviewText: These are perfect for bedroom table lights. They are small, have cell charger outlets, they are dimmable, and give off plenty of light. They match the bathroom lights, too. Love!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very attractive and functional lamps. I use them as bedroom end table lamps. They are attractive and look more expensive than what I paid. The built-in USB charging ports are a great feature. I recommend this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Little Lamps!
reviews.reviewText: Bought lamps for a short term rental. They are perfect. They do not take up much space on the nightstand. They were easy to assemble. The light can be adjusted from dim to bright. Love the seeded glass! They were very reasonably priced for the set. 10 out of 10!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice looking lamps.
reviews.reviewText: The only reason I didn't give this item five stars is because the shade allows the light bulb to be far too bright. While sitting there, the light was so bright in the corner of my eye that it was highly distracting. If you don't mind that, then you'll love these lamps. Personally, I couldn't see with the light so bright in my eyes. Even on the dimmest of light options, it was still bright. Otherwise, a nice product and very pretty.

reviews.reviewText: Great light. Adjustable with enough wattage for bedside reading. Looks good on nightstands. Two USB outlets are a plus.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: They are amazing! Great quality and you can dim them or brighten them with a twist of the finger and get 4 different brightness from low to high.Love them and would highly recommend this product! They are very chic as well!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars The light's are 6 months old and 1 stopped working
reviews.reviewText: I actually loved these lights. Unfortunately, one of the lights no longer works properly. The usb ports in the base still work, but the light no longer does. I've changed the recommended bulbs twice, so it is not the bulbs. Sometimes when I turn it on, the light will work, other times it takes a few minutes, sometimes it will turn on but if I try to turn the light up to full strength it stops working, and sometimes not at all. It looks like there is only a 3 month guarantee on the lamps. At over $100.00 for the two table lamps, the quality should be better and the lamp should last longer.
